// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1054 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 83612667-3421-5442-9e19-310048eb265a

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
